<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: SameOme AlpineKnight</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-24 15:44:24</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>i know paladin might not be able to do as much dmg as a worrior in a battle with the same 2hs weapon.  but, there is a lot more fun playing a paladin than worrior and trust me it is true.  being able to heal and buff ourselves is the best advantage a pally has over a worrior.  ppl keep telling me "pallies can't solo".  oh yeah?  i soloed from lvl1 to lvl30, then started soloing again from lvl40, and now i am lvl47.  of course, being able to get the better weapon than most of the same lvls is what it takes to achive that.  i used a blade of xalgoz since low 20's,when most of the same lvls were using GZ, RCs.  i had full set of Ro or better at lvl35 and managed to get the fbss at the same lvl.  i finally got an Arbitors Combine Greatsword at lvl45, when most of the same lvls are using the xalgoz or the mithril two hander.  getting more DW Volorium is my goal, i only have a DW helm now.  with the gears i have, i can solo a lot better than most of the same lvl melee classes.  worrior can only shout for "lvl?? worrior seekin group" at all time.  they missed all the fun soloing and being able to caste.  you never hear a paladin asking for heal or buffs (unless it is in a group battle).  pallies can't solo?  i bet you not.  <BR>
<BR>
back to the topic.  yes pallies always have the hardest quest in game.  killing naggie and vox ain't ez nor fun.  FA is not the greatest weapon for paladins either.  Though i would still try to get the FA if i can, it is about the fun you will have when holding it out-damaging most same lvl worriors (never say all).  FA is now a 1hs as most of you might have known.  for those of you think this sword suck and not worth the time, tell me why you play this game and show me if you have a better weapon than this.  i doubt it.  for those ppl who managed to complete their class only quest, they won't be saying things like that cuz they know what kind of fun they had, and the proudness of using the weapon they obtained.  i bet they will respect all other classes' class only weapon but not saying 'this thing suck, it ain't the best'.  get yours first and tell me that, i doubt you can if you are such a person.  anyways...  <BR>
<BR>
if you play on vallon zek you probably know who i am, you either like or dislike me and i know.  yes i was the one who sold you the bone chips,  the one who auctioning CB belts in gfay for you to twink your twinks, but now, i am reaching the high lvl and is one of the best trader on the server.  i would like to get some help of the FA quest if you are high enough lvl and play on VZ.  i will pay all of those back within my limit (and trust me you will be surprised on what i can do).  send me a email if you wish to,  ywu1103@hotmail.com  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
SameOme AlpineKnight<BR>
47th Paladin (and proud of it)<BR>
on Vallon Zek</font></td></tr></table>
